---
const destinations = [
  {
    name: 'Machu Picchu',
    location: 'Cusco',
    image: 'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1587595431973-160d0d94add1?w=600&q=80',
    duration: '2-5 días',
    price: 299,
    rating: 4.9,
    href: '/destinos/cusco-machu-picchu',
  },
  {
    name: 'Lago Titicaca',
    location: 'Puno',
    image: 'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1580619305218-8423a7ef79b4?w=600&q=80',
    duration: '2-3 días',
    price: 199,
    rating: 4.8,
    href: '/destinos',
  },
  {
    name: 'Líneas de Nazca',
    location: 'Ica',
    image: 'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1599499462209-5cf308ead061?w=600&q=80',
    duration: '1-2 días',
    price: 149,
    rating: 4.7,
    href: '/destinos',
  },
  {
    name: 'Amazonas',
    location: 'Iquitos',
    image: 'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1516026672322-bc52d61a55d5?w=600&q=80',
    duration: '3-5 días',
    price: 349,
    rating: 4.9,
    href: '/destinos',
  },
  {
    name: 'Cañón del Colca',
    location: 'Arequipa',
    image: 'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1580399581268-478e4e4ae1f5?w=600&q=80',
    duration: '2-3 días',
    price: 179,
    rating: 4.8,
    href: '/destinos',
  },
  {
    name: 'Huacachina',
    location: 'Ica',
    image: 'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1531065208531-4036c0dba3ca?w=600&q=80',
    duration: '1-2 días',
    price: 129,
    rating: 4.6,
    href: '/destinos',
  },
];
---

<section class="section" id="destinos">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header">
      <span class="section-label">Destinos Destacados</span>
      <h2>Explora los mejores destinos del Perú</h2>
      <p>Desde las cumbres de los Andes hasta la selva amazónica, descubre lugares que te dejarán sin aliento.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="dest-grid">
      {destinations.map(dest => (
        <a href={dest.href} class="card dest-card">
          <div class="card-img">
            <img src={dest.image} alt={dest.name} loading="lazy" />
            <div class="dest-overlay">
              <span class="badge badge-accent">{dest.duration}</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="card-body">
            <div class="dest-header">
              <h3>{dest.name}</h3>
              <div class="rating">★ {dest.rating}</div>
            </div>
            <p class="dest-location">📍 {dest.location}</p>
            <div class="dest-footer">
              <span class="price-label">Desde</span>
              <span class="price">${dest.price}</span>
              <span class="price-label">por persona</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </a>
      ))}
    </div>

    <div class="section-cta">
      <a href="/destinos" class="btn btn-outline">Ver todos los destinos →</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .dest-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 2rem;
  }
  .dest-card { display: block; }
  .dest-overlay {
    position: absolute;
    top: 1rem;
    right: 1rem;
  }
  .dest-header {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: flex-start;
    margin-bottom: 0.35rem;
  }
  .dest-header h3 { font-size: 1.15rem; }
  .dest-location {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--text-light);
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }
  .dest-footer {
    display: flex;
    align-items: baseline;
    gap: 0.35rem;
    padding-top: 0.75rem;
    border-top: 1px solid #f1f5f9;
  }
  .dest-footer .price { font-size: 1.3rem; }
  .section-cta {
    text-align: center;
    margin-top: 2.5rem;
  }
  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .dest-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
  }
  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .dest-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }
</style>
